{"tid":2345213,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係香港玩過LARP?","createTime":"2020-12-29T10:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T11:15:41.000Z","uid":71543,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"458890070c43a5645b0fbb38f2f3c6fb0201ee6d","tid":2345213,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"直接偷之前啲POST既介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我只係想知香港啲LARP鋪好唔好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">咩係LARP?</span></strong><br />\n「LARP 的全稱是 Live Action Role Playing，即實境動作角色扮演遊戲，亦稱為實境角色扮演遊戲。參與者在扮演角色的同時須要實際的做出動作行為。玩家的目標是在現實環境的限制中追求虛構環境扮演，同時與其他扮演角色互動。玩家行動的結果可能是由遊戲的規則或玩家之間的協商一致所產生的。」(引自維基)<br />\n通常LARP都係以兇殺案為主題，玩家需要一同推理案情，而兇手當然要掩飾自己身份，但過程中既重點都係享受扮演。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">點樣玩LARP?</span></strong><br />\n1.遊戲前大家都會收到遊戲說明同各自既角色劇本<br />\n各位玩家要仔細閱讀說明同劇本，揣摩角色性格，以及對角色的各項資料設定都有大致既掌握。<br />\n2.遊戲進行中，大家都要完全投入角色之中<br />\nLARP係實時角色扮演遊戲，每個人既發言舉止都應該要符合返角色設定，一方面咁樣先可以最大化呢種遊戲既特色，另一方面其實亦方便各位可以透過各種蛛絲馬跡去尋找真相。<br />\n3.遊戲中唔可以做出跳脫角色(out-game)既言行<br />\n例如係直接將劇本展示、話「我劇本冇寫」等等。<br />\n4.享受過程，扮演優先<br />\n唔好好左要羸出遊戲就將扮演元素放於次要，就算查唔出真相/好早已被鎖定你係真兇，都要堅持扮演到遊戲結束。<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"0aab35e87b57d1286a49f6bdf175064604540be5","tid":2345213,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1db69ad9ba8d8c1e97963803914e58c2231739","tid":2345213,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc47f3513400a735e76c1eb7fdfa7cdad033602","tid":2345213,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bbc14c0a65ac5c5b7cfd8ecdb1c9ee35391a4b","tid":2345213,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28f746000445fdb5454d74af00ebd6ba2aa84ea","tid":2345213,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"睇台灣鹿人佢地好似玩得好好笑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a96434a19bd73acefca65737e6c24c2a6950b9","tid":2345213,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d28f746000445fdb5454d74af00ebd6ba2aa84ea","tid":2345213,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"睇台灣鹿人佢地好似玩得好好笑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"係呀屌！我都有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣啲鋪頭好似好用心<br />\n但我驚香港啲larp鋪都係hea做<br />\n搞到冇咗搜證嚇人橋段<br />\n幾年前玩密室逃脫中晒伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367ba165f407fa2a262d59109c84f6132f47fea6","tid":2345213,"uid":59868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47a96434a19bd73acefca65737e6c24c2a6950b9","tid":2345213,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d28f746000445fdb5454d74af00ebd6ba2aa84ea","tid":2345213,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"睇台灣鹿人佢地好似玩得好好笑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"係呀屌！我都有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/c